---
import WhatsAppButton from './WhatsAppButton.astro'
---

<div class='relative isolate px-6 pt-[calc(var(--navbar-height)-48px)] lg:px-8'>
  <!-- Top gradient blob -->
  <div
    aria-hidden='true'
    class='absolute inset-x-0 -top-40 -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden blur-3xl sm:-top-80'>
    <div
      style='clip-path: polygon(74.1% 44.1%, 100% 61.6%, 97.5% 26.9%, 85.5% 0.1%, 80.7% 2%, 72.5% 32.5%, 60.2% 62.4%, 52.4% 68.1%, 47.5% 58.3%, 45.2% 34.5%, 27.5% 76.7%, 0.1% 64.9%, 17.9% 100%, 27.6% 76.8%, 76.1% 97.7%, 74.1% 44.1%)'
      class='relative left-[calc(50%-11rem)] aspect-1155/678 w-144.5 -translate-x-1/2 rotate-30 bg-linear-to-tr from-sky-400 to-sky-600 opacity-30 sm:left-[calc(50%-30rem)] sm:w-288.75'>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero content -->
  <div class='mx-auto max-w-3xl py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-40'>
    <!-- Badge pill -->
    <div class='hidden sm:mb-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center'>
      <h1
        class='relative rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm/6 text-gray-600 ring-1 ring-gray-900/20'>
        Posicionamiento Web en Barcelona
      </h1>
    </div>
    <!-- Centered text -->
    <div class='text-center'>
      <p
        class='text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-petrol-900 sm:text-7xl'>
        Deja de perder clientes frente a tu competencia
      </p>
      <p
        class='mt-8 text-lg font-medium text-pretty text-gray-500 sm:text-xl/8'>
        En Barcelona, o eres el primero o eres el secreto de tu competencia.
        Domina las búsquedas de Google, multiplica tus contactos y pon tu web a
        trabajar de verdad. Si te buscan, que te encuentren a ti primero.
      </p>
      <!-- CTAs -->
      <div class='mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6'>
        <WhatsAppButton text='Analiza mi web ahora' />
        <a
          href='#proceso'
          class='text-sm/6 font-semibold text-gray-900'>
          Cómo trabajo <span aria-hidden='true'>→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom gradient blob -->
  <div
    aria-hidden='true'
    class='absolute inset-x-0 top-[calc(100%-13rem)] -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden blur-3xl sm:top-[calc(100%-30rem)]'>
    <div
      style='clip-path: polygon(74.1% 44.1%, 100% 61.6%, 97.5% 26.9%, 85.5% 0.1%, 80.7% 2%, 72.5% 32.5%, 60.2% 62.4%, 52.4% 68.1%, 47.5% 58.3%, 45.2% 34.5%, 27.5% 76.7%, 0.1% 64.9%, 17.9% 100%, 27.6% 76.8%, 76.1% 97.7%, 74.1% 44.1%)'
      class='relative left-[calc(50%+3rem)] aspect-1155/678 w-144.5 -translate-x-1/2 bg-linear-to-tr from-sky-400 to-sky-600 opacity-30 sm:left-[calc(50%+36rem)] sm:w-288.75'>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
